<TEXT>&#2;<DATELINE>2016-04-08</DATELINE><TITLE>Smart durable and self-healing textile coatings</TITLE><BODY>The durability of textiles can be endangered in different ways. Various treatments are used to protect textiles against degradation or damage or even to restore or repair the initial properties. Other technologies are still under investigation. In this chapter an overview is presented of the work done in our laboratory in the area of smart coatings protecting textiles.&#3;</BODY></TEXT>